text:
Sparkly～ and frilly～ and fluffy～,
It's like these clothes are from a dream or somethin'～!!

Haha, indeed, stage costumes feel
a bit fantastical, don't they.

Yeah～
And so I'll wear these clothes, and turn that dream into reality!

That's the spirit.
If it's Kogane, I'm sure you can do it. Absolutely.

Nfufu～... If I've got Producer's stamp of approval, 
that'll fill me with confidence～

Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
What kind of dream will you show me, I wonder.

Leave it to me! I'll train like m'life depends on it,
And do m'best at jobs so...

An' wearing these clothes,
I'll show you the most amazin'performance in the universe...!
